      <title>需求疲软有助于保护冬季库存，欧洲天然气价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/europe-gas-falls-as-sluggish-demand-helps-preserve-winter-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格下跌，因为对燃料的持续低需求有助于维持该地区的库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/europe-gas-falls-as-sluggish-demand-helps-preserve-winter-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 07:36:33 GMT</pubDate>
